{"tid":1663762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑商場新都城打壓黃店","createTime":"2019-10-19T15:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T03:15:19.000Z","uid":33586,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0425d6d7a88ebccf5e8496a9b23f5dca54fb6b2","tid":1663762,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"本身間舖外牆同玻璃貼滿哂文宣 但係無啦啦係痴走<br />\n加上如果租約期滿好多時間舖頭會貼啲紙出嚟提早講聲<br />\n但係佢無啦啦結業並且貼咗以下嘅通告出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSVOvUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSVOvUF.jpg&h=604f385c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到網上有人話佢係偽黃店 因為老闆好遲先表態<br />\n但係貼得文宣出嚟 就有得失一方嘅後果 <br />\n佢表完態 又唔係多人食咗 如果老闆係藍 點解唔揀唔表態呢 <br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要關注事件 比人知道一定support同路人<br />\n商場基於咩理由要求移除文宣poster 而貼係門口餐牌嘅poster又可以保留？<br />\n結業係咪同表態有關？"},{"pid":"ac4390c092622689ddd934671d66d52d9b2de15a","tid":1663762,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6197f9310fb1a06e27afbc1537ddc222d16d5c3","tid":1663762,"uid":18470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"之前呢間話係藍扮黄喎"},{"pid":"8feb77a557280c3660227d005cc0860e31cfd079","tid":1663762,"uid":133086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"有偽黃絲店想發國難財 荃灣人入黎！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1625829/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1625829/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6ff5ea20d96684bf9f5f506d793ea74b42f49de1","tid":1663762,"uid":33586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631341/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631341/page/1</a>